Class Page

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.cms.component.page.Page
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.i2rd.cms.PageMetaInformation, java.io.Serializable, PageProperties, PageElement, Trashable

    @PageElementModelConfiguration(supportsLabels=true,
                               assignedByDefault=true,
                               iconPath="cms/icons/x32/html_page.png",
                               name="cms.CommonCmsText-Page")
 @Categorized(category=Page)
public class Page
extends java.lang.Object
implements PageProperties, PageElement
    Represents a Page for a site.

    This Page implementation delegates to other PageElements.

    Russ Tennant (russ@proteus.co)
